review_blob: My old dog got into them the dirty bastard but for $10 a doz I dont give a shit. Not that bad tasting. Good beer if youve got fines to pay off but still want to have a good time.
Tastes like somebody put a cigarette out in almost every can. Cheap as hell though so if you and the missus cant afford Double Brown pick up a few of these babies. Best drunk from a tube.

At roughly $1 NZ (around 20 cents US) for a 330ml 4% tin you can get drunk without blowing your benefit. Also comes in 440ml 6 packs for when youre really on the skids. Tastes a bit crap so drink it as fast as possible.
If youre living on the bones of your ass and trying to fight off the shakes this will do the trick. Otherwise it should be avoided at all costs.
